text: Aaron E. Pollock (born February 12, 1967) is an American rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:American male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from San Francisco
